File: packages/service-core/src/services/destination/destination.service.ts — the update() override.

Replace the separate withTransaction call with ctx.tx propagation:
```typescript
// BEFORE (Phase 3 - T-017)
await withTransaction(async (tx) => {
  await this.model.updateDescendantPaths(parentId, oldPath, newPath, tx);
});

// AFTER (Phase 4)
if (resolvedCtx.tx) {
  await this.model.updateDescendantPaths(parentId, oldPath, newPath, resolvedCtx.tx);
} else {
  await withTransaction(async (tx) => {
    await this.model.updateDescendantPaths(parentId, oldPath, newPath, tx);
  });
}
```

This ensures that when update() is called inside withServiceTransaction, the path cascade runs in the SAME transaction — no separate inner transaction.

